<title>USA: Salomon Inc Q3 net off, well below estimate.</title>
<headline>Salomon Inc Q3 net off, well below estimate.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1996-10-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>1996			1995</p>
<p> Shr primary		$0.88		    $2.36</p>
<p> Shr diluted		 0.85		     2.10</p>
<p> Net			112,000		  268,000</p>
<p> Net revs		 816,000		1,181,000</p>
<p> Avg shrs primary     105,500		  106,600</p>
<p> Avg shrs diluted     120,600		  125,400</p>
<p>(All Data Above 000s Except Per Share Numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE: First Call Q3 consensus estimate $1.19/shr.  </p>
<p>	  NINE MONTHS</p>
<p> Shr primary		$5.90		    $2.22</p>
<p> Shr diluted		 5.41		     2.19</p>
<p> Net			679,000		  289,000</p>
<p> Net revs	     3,228,000		2,325,000</p>
<p> Avg shrs primary     105,800		  106,500</p>
<p> Avg shrs diluted     121,000		  125,300</p>
<p>NOTE: 1996 Q3 and nine month results include pre-tax gain $48 million ($31 million after taxes) on sale of Mortgage Co Ltd.  </p>
<p>Q3 total revenues $1.96 billion versus $2.54 billion.</p>
<p>Nine month total revenues $6.79 billion versus $6.56 billion.</p>
<p>-- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610</p>
